ENCODING MODES

OLED, 8 pix/byte, BW
- Bitmap for OLED
- Vertical byte
- 8 pixels in 1 byte
- Black & White

8 pix/byte, BW
- Horizontal byte
- 8 pixels in 1 byte
- Black & White

1 pix/byte, BW
- Horizontal byte
- 1 pixel in 1 byte
- Black & White

1 pix/byte, Gray
- Horizontal byte
- 1 pixel in 1 byte
- Grayscale 8 bit (0-255)

1 pix/int16 (RGB565)
- Horizontal int16
- 1 pixel in int16
- RGB colors RGB565
- RRRRRGGGGGGBBBBB

1 pix/int32 (RGB888)
- Horizontal int32
- 1 pixel in int32
- RGB colors RGB888
- RRRRRRRRGGGGGGGGBBBBBBBB